<section class="section" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem__layout">
      <div class="problem__header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why this matters</p>
        <h2 id="problem-heading">
          LinkedIn is your highest-value B2B channel.<br />
          Most companies are wasting it.
        </h2>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem__body">
        <p class="problem__lead">
          Over 65 million decision-makers are active on LinkedIn. Four out of five LinkedIn members
          drive business decisions. B2B marketers consistently rate it as their strongest channel
          for lead generation, thought leadership, and brand awareness.
        </p>
        <p>
          And yet — company pages go weeks without a post. Executive profiles read like old CVs.
          Ad budgets burn through audiences with no clear targeting strategy. Content gets published
          without a plan and earns nothing.
        </p>
        <p class="problem__close">
          The gap between what LinkedIn can deliver for a B2B company and what most companies
          actually get from it is significant. <strong>Closing that gap is what we do.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .problem__header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .problem__body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .problem__lead {
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    color: var(--color-deep-navy);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .problem__body p {
    color: var(--color-slate);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .problem__close {
    color: var(--color-dark) !important;
  }

  .problem__close strong {
    color: var(--color-blue);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .problem__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
  }
</style>
